- The string parameter `text` and `pattern` consist only of lowercase English letters.
- The length of the string parameter `text` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100000.
- The length of the string parameter `pattern` is equal to 2.
- The long result is the maximum number of times the string parameter `pattern` can occur as a subsequence of the modified string parameter `text`.
- The character from the string parameter `pattern` can be added exactly once anywhere in the string parameter `text`.
- The character can be added at the beginning or at the end of the string parameter `text`.